attributes.description: Thermax Limited offers solutions to energy, environment and chemical sectors. The Company’s portfolio includes boilers and heaters, absorption chillers/ heat pumps, power plants, solar equipment, air pollution control equipment/system, water and waste recycle plant, ion exchange resins and performance chemicals and related services. [1]
